{"tid":1748461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柒婆：拒聽建制停區選，靜等明日民意逆轉硬推廿三條","createTime":"2019-11-23T16:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T17:05:29.000Z","uid":335157,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3ebb6e80693cf308550d128963b9720468d2d3","tid":1748461,"uid":335157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"[i]麻煩睇睇內文<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日連登一直分化區選<br />\n一批就肯定係mon post狗<br />\n另一批就係熱狗 垃圾城邦派<br />\n<br />\n你以為害撚到泛民？<br />\n<br />\n泛民政混選唔到就去做社區主任，做翻本行<br />\n<br />\n黃色版塊輸咗係成個香港變新疆<br />\n<br />\n區選係制度下最展現到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意基礎</span></strong></span>嘅方法 <br />\n<br />\n區選就係你地口中嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">五區公投</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔理你幾憎泛民 泛民點樣逼害獨派<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">明年仲有立法會選舉 泛民明年都唔會割</span></span><br />\n<br />\n敵人的敵人就係朋友<br />\n<br />\n如果今次你投<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">白票/建制</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n政府就係因為你地嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">所作所為</span></span></strong><br />\n同外國講<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">大部分市民支持止暴制亂<br />\n<br />\n市民反感暴力違法佔路</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">一句講曬：<br />\n分化區選撚=藍屍</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2414d5260a691d08332f0a92aabd6a819e093e0c","tid":1748461,"uid":157938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投票踢走保皇黨 就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投票踢走保皇黨 就係咁簡單"},{"p